Plot Outline:
The Sisterhood of Traveling Pants 2 (2008)
In "Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants 2," based on Ann Brashares&#039; best-selling series of novels, four young women continue 
the journey toward adulthood that began with "The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants." Now three years later, these lifelong 
friends embark on separate paths for their first year of college and the summer beyond, but remain in touch by sharing their 
experiences with each other as they always have-with honesty and humor. Discovering their individual strengths, fears, talents 
and capacity for love through the choices they make, they come to value more than ever the bond they share and the immeasurable 
power of their friendship.
